OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine with sunny spells
OL,6,Finitially, but tending to become
OL,7,Fcloudier from the northwest as
OL,8,Foccasional rain makes hesitant
OL,9,Fprogress eastwards, eventually heavier
OL,10,Fin places. Very warm and humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith rain and showers likely during
OL,14,Fthe evening before easing and turning
OL,15,Fdrier and more settled by the morning.
OL,16,FWinds easing overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
