OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy for a time, becoming
OL,6,Fdrier and brighter with sunny spells
OL,7,Flater. Temperatures slightly lower
OL,8,Fthan previous days. Winds light and
OL,9,Fvariable.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,12,Fdrier and brighter with sunny spells
OL,13,Flate, ahead of isolated thunderstorms
OL,14,Fpossible Monday. Dry with sunny spells
OL,15,Fon Tuesday. Temperatures climbing,
OL,16,Fvery warm and humid.
